==Description==
The '''Purple Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]] first encountered in [[Johto]].

==Details==
The Purple Shard can be used, alongside [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at the [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Purple Shard appears in the Underground as a 4x2 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:PurpleShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Purple Shards can be used together with other [[Shards]] to purchase the following items:
